sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Researcher
    actor Owner as Data Owner
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant API as Backend
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant Qdrant as Qdrant
    participant Celery as Celery

    User->>FE: Click "Report Incorrect" on result
    FE->>User: Show feedback form (pre-filled)
    User->>FE: Select correct species, enter description
    FE->>API: POST /api/v1/feedback
    API->>PG: Insert feedback (status: pending)
    API-->>FE: { feedback_id, status: pending }
    FE->>User: Show confirmation

    Note over Owner: Later...
    Owner->>FE: Open Feedback Inbox
    FE->>API: GET /api/v1/feedback/inbox
    API->>PG: Query pending feedback
    API-->>FE: [{ feedback items }]

    Owner->>FE: Review item, click "Accept"
    FE->>API: PATCH /api/v1/feedback/{id} (status: accepted)

    API->>PG: Update strain species_id
    API->>PG: Create audit_log entry
    API->>PG: Mark affected qdrant_index_state → is_active=FALSE
    API->>Celery: Queue re-index for affected segments
    API->>PG: Update feedback status, reviewed_at

    API-->>FE: { status: accepted }
    FE->>Owner: Show confirmation

    Celery->>Qdrant: Re-extract features + upsert

    User->>FE: View "My Feedback"
    FE->>API: GET /api/v1/feedback
    API-->>FE: [{ item: status=accepted, review_note }]
